{
  "stem": "9665.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyway, so to go back to Czechoslovakia-- my friend was a friend of the trade commissioner by the name of [INAUDIBLE] Lachman, who introduced me to him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He got imprisoned in 1949 in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he got imprisoned by doing things which was not supposed to be done.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--flags.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they thought this was because he was a spy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, my friend was not pro-communist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was Catholic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not only that, he was very anti-communist.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The same time, we had some Jewish people which couldn't get out of Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had an organization-- we had an organization-- we had a transport company in Holland called, Van Gend and Loos.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Van Gend and Loos-- and I will spell that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "V-A-N, one word.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Gend is G-E-N-D.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Loos is L-O-O-S.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Still the largest-- one of the largest transport company in Holland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They went up and down with-- it was one of the first with they have a double containers-- [INAUDIBLE] double trucks, and so on, and so on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I needed some goods to get out there from these Jewish people, and he helped me with it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This started in '47-- no, '48, when the communists came in there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was imprisoned in-- in middle or late '49.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we got him out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We got these people-- sorry, we got these people, whenever they want to get out of Czechoslovakia, we got it out with Van Gend and Loos.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The man was imprisoned the second half of 1949, accused of being a spy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "At the same time, there were two people in Budapest which were accused of being a spy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "One was [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Voglers, ?] and the other was [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Sanders. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Jan Laos, Jan Laos, was working for AKU, which was second-- second or third large organization in Holland.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
